    <item>
      <title>美国对 SAP 和 Carahsoft 展开价格操纵调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-probing-tech-firms-sap-carahsoft-for-potential-price-fixing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国软件开发商 SAP SE、产品经销商 Carahsoft Technology Corp. 和其他公司正在接受美国官员的调查，原因是它们可能在过去十年中合谋向政府机构收取过高费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-probing-tech-firms-sap-carahsoft-for-potential-price-fixing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 03:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩公司称，到 2027 年，人工智能市场规模将飙升至近 1 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ai-market-will-surge-to-near-1-trillion-by-2027-bain-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝恩公司表示，随着人工智能技术的快速应用颠覆企业和经济，全球人工智能相关产品市场正在迅速膨胀，到 2027 年将达到 9900 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ai-market-will-surge-to-near-1-trillion-by-2027-bain-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 向白宫推介前所未有的数据中心建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/openai-pitched-white-house-on-unprecedented-data-center-buildout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 向拜登政府强调了对大型数据中心的需求，每个数据中心所用的电量可能相当于整个城市，并称这种前所未有的扩张是开发更先进的人工智能模型和与中国竞争的必要条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/openai-pitched-white-house-on-unprecedented-data-center-buildout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 23:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福特斯丘斥资 28 亿美元为铁矿石卡车提供电气化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/fortescue-inks-2-8-billion-deal-to-electrify-iron-ore-trucks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球第四大铁矿石生产商 Fortescue Ltd. 将斥资 28 亿美元，将其在西澳大利亚的三分之二的运输卡车和设备更换为电动卡车和设备，以减少柴油消耗并实现雄心勃勃的减排目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/fortescue-inks-2-8-billion-deal-to-electrify-iron-ore-trucks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 22:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国金融科技公司寻求成为伦敦金属交易所标志性交易大厅的会员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/lme-trading-floor-gets-boost-as-us-fintech-firm-seeks-membership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融服务公司 Clear Street 正在寻求加入伦敦金属交易所的公开喊价交易大厅，此举将增强标志性“圈”的前景。近年来，该交易所的交易量出现下滑，且大批交易员离场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/lme-trading-floor-gets-boost-as-us-fintech-firm-seeks-membership</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 20:44:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
